body.name: kleankin Slim Bathroom Storage Cabinet, Tall Bathroom Cabinet, Narrow Linen Tower with Acrylic Door, Drawer and Shelves, Gray
features: Multiple Storage: Our storage bathroom cabinet has a three-layer shelf on the top, a drawer in the middle, and a bottom shelf with a board inside to provide ample storage space for the kitchens, bathrooms, and living rooms.
Space Saving Design: Modern design allows our cabinet to provide maximum capacity in narrow spaces. It is an excellent choice as a bathroom cabinet beside a sink or toilet.
Quality Material: Constructed of P2 grade MDF board, this storage cabinet restroom decor is stable enough for daily use. Its painted surface makes cleaning and maintenance easy.
Secure Design: A great storage space organizer, this solid, tall storage cabinet features an anti-toppling design, letting you attach it to the wall for added safety.
Storage Cabinet Info: Overall Dimensions: 15.75" L x 10.75" W x 67.5" H. Weight Capacity: 11 lbs. (Per Shelf), 4.4 lbs. (Per Drawer), 59.4 lbs. (Total).
body.description: Are you still worried about not finding a suitable place to store things? This simple storage cabinet with doors can display décor and hide away unmentionables. Made into a slim tower design, it will fit into a wealth of spaces, making it great for creating space in any room. Quality material and an anti-toppling design ensure its stability and safety. When you go with a kleankin storage cabinet you can maximize storage and minimize clutter.
